### 2. Chat Text Area, Plan/Build Buttons, Play/Stop Buttons

All defined in **`/home/glompy/Desktop/ASTROCYTECH/Agent_X/ui/src/App.jsx`**.

#### a) Chat Text Area (`<textarea>`)

**Lines 1285-1293** in the JSX return:

```jsx
<textarea
  ref={inputRef}
  className="input-box"
  placeholder="Type a message... (Enter to send, Shift+Enter for newline)"
  value={input}
  onChange={(e) => setInput(e.target.value)}
  onKeyDown={handleKeyDown}
  rows={2}
/>
```

State is held in `input` (line 555: `const [input, setInput] = useState("")`).  
Sending is handled by `sendMessage()` (lines 1002-1142) and `handleKeyDown` (lines 1144-1149) which fires on Enter (without Shift).

The textarea is wrapped in `<div className="input-bar">` which also contains the **input-actions** buttons.

#### b) Plan / Build Toggle Buttons

**Lines 1261-1281** in the JSX:

```jsx
<div className="mode-bar">
