#### c) Layout Summary (visual)

```
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
|  .menubar (Session | Agent | System | Help)                       |
+--------+----------------------------+------+----------------------+
|        |                            |      |                      |
| .status|  .chat-area                |resize|  .activity-panel-wrap|
